    "在 opensubtitles.com 注册并在 Consumers 创建一个 API Consumer 获取 API Key。Key 与账号仅保存在本机钥匙串。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Register at opensubtitles.com and create an API Consumer under Consumers to get an API Key. The key and account are stored only in this device's keychain."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "在 themoviedb.org → 设置 → API 免费申请 v3 Key，粘贴后即可加载真实海报。Key 仅保存在本机。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Get a free v3 key at themoviedb.org → Settings → API, then paste it to load real posters. The key stays on this device."
